## ğŸ¯ Project Objective
Analyze sales, discounts, and profits in a retail store dataset to uncover actionable business insights and identify areas for strategic improvement.

---

## ğŸ—‚ï¸ Dataset
- Source: [Sample Supermarket Dataset - Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/bravehart101/sample-supermarket-dataset)
